    "Deep learning promises better performance compared to other machine learning methods.",
    "However, the computational complexity of deep learning is resource-intensive.",
    "With the development of future computational speed, computational complexity constraints can be overcome.English is the largest language dataset available for NER research because English is the most widely spoken language globally.",
